      <title>Show HN: Eonfall – A new third-person co-op action game built for the web</title>
      <link>https://eonfall.com</link>
      <description>Hi all, I&amp;#x27;m excited to share Eonfall with Hacker News Community!&lt;p&gt;It&amp;#x27;s been 2-years in the making built by a 2 man team. Eonfall, is a new third-person co-op action game with rogue-lite elements built exclusively for the web! We&amp;#x27;ve finally reached a release candidate state and set our official public release date for Jan 15th! The game&amp;#x27;s current version 5.0.0-beta is live and available to test play today!&lt;p&gt;Unity game engine was used to develop the game along with other services to handle the backend, and Nuxt 3 + Nuxt UI to handle the front-end.&lt;p&gt;We welcome any and all questions, feedback &amp;amp; suggestions!&lt;p&gt;Thanks all, Jon</description>
